Loader for Basis Universal GPU Texture Codec. * * Basis Universal is a "supercompressed" GPU texture and texture video * compression system that outputs a highly compressed intermediate file format * (.basis) that can be quickly transcoded to a wide variety of GPU texture * compression formats. * * This loader parallelizes the transcoding process across a configurable number * of web workers, before transferring the transcoded compressed texture back * to the main thread.
